      "description": "Meet your next great adventure. This stunning machine rolls into your life with an air of quiet confidence \u2014 every curve deliberate, every surface catching the light just so. Slide into the driver's seat and you're wrapped in an interior that feels untouched by time, the kind of cabin that still carries that almost-forgotten new-car magic. Under the hood, she hums with purpose, eager and responsive, ready to devour open roads and city streets alike. This is the car you've been picturing in your driveway, the one that makes neighbors pause on their morning walk. Opportunities like this don't wait \u2014 she's priced to move and ready to begin her next chapter with someone who truly appreciates her.",
      "price": 43500.0,
